---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Baldwinson">
	<section class="hero-section relative flex min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem] text-center">
			<h1 class="hero-primary text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.01em] text-foreground sm:text-[2.125rem] sm:leading-[1.15] lg:text-[2.75rem] lg:leading-[1.15]">
				Building durable systems at the intersection of technology, ethics, and governance.
			</h1>
			
			<p class="hero-secondary mt-[1em] text-[1rem] leading-[1.5] text-foreground/70 sm:text-[1.125rem] lg:text-[1.25rem]">
				Independent work across software engineering, institutional design, and applied ethics.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/20 px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-32 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem]">
			<p class="mb-12 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground/60">
				Areas of work
			</p>
			
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<a href="/work" class="group block">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground/80 sm:text-lg">
						Work
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
						Software systems, organizational structure, and operational scale.
					</p>
				</a>
				
				<a href="/insights" class="group block">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground/80 sm:text-lg">
						Insights
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
						Analysis and position papers on technology governance.
					</p>
				</a>
				
				<a href="/ethics" class="group block">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground/80 sm:text-lg">
						Ethics
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
						Nonprofit initiative for engineers and technology decision-makers.
					</p>
				</a>
				
				<a href="/apps" class="group block">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-medium text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground/80 sm:text-lg">
						Apps
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
						Applied software projects developed outside of client or advisory work.
					</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/20 px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-32 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem]">
			<p class="mb-12 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground/60">
				Selected focus areas
			</p>
			<ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
				<li>Large-scale software systems</li>
				<li>Organizational design under constraint</li>
				<li>Technology governance and ethics</li>
				<li>Long-term system durability</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/20 px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-32 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem]">
			<p class="mb-12 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground/60">
				Recent writing
			</p>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<a href="/insights" class="group block">
					<h3 class="mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-foreground/80 sm:text-base">
						Coming soon
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground/60">
						Essays and analysis on technology governance.
					</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/20 px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-32 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem]">
			<p class="mb-8 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground/60">
				Current focus
			</p>
			<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
				Current focus includes work on long-lived software systems, organizational durability, and ethical constraints in technology decision-making.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-t border-border/20 px-6 py-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-32 lg:px-12">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem]">
			<p class="mb-8 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground/60">
				Contact
			</p>
			<p class="text-sm text-foreground/70 sm:text-base">
				For inquiries related to advisory, collaboration, or institutional work.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
